/e3a2/582836_large.png?m=1658121410", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d088/e3a2/582836_xlarge.png?m=1658121410", "created": 1653547945, "last_modified": 1658121410}, "last_reply_by": "scruel", "last_touched": 1665725841, "title": "把每一 bug 都当最后一 bug 来修, 然后也不要重构", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/886806", "created": 1665709188, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1665709188, "replies": 67, "id": 886806}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1659331259", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1659331259", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 51314, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1659331259", "stars": 8023, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 220603, "username": "liuidetmks", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/liuidetmks", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e540/71e7/220603_mini.png?m=1665710527", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e540/71e7/220603_normal.png?m=1665710527", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e540/71e7/220603_large.png?m=1665710527", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e540/71e7/220603_xlarge.png?m=1665710527", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e540/71e7/220603_xlarge.png?m=1665710527", "created": 1489372952, "last_modified": 1665710527}, "last_reply_by": "cat9life", "last_touched": 1665725821, "title": "为什么国外一个小公司做出来的东西，大公司会买账？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/886657", "created": 1665646616, "deleted": 0, "content": "比如 yubikey ，一个小公司做的东西，MS gogole 都支持.\r\n\r\n国内感觉就是大公司喜欢搞自己的一套， 自己造也不会用你的。", "content_rendered": "比如 yubikey ，一个小公司做的东西，MS gogole 都支持.<br /><br />国内感觉就是大公司喜欢搞自己的一套， 自己造也不会用你的。", "last_modified": 1665646616, "replies": 64, "id": 886657}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1635654723", "name": "bb", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1635654723", "title": "宽带症候群", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb", "topics": 11562, "footer": "", "header": "网速很重要。比快更快。", "title_alternative": "Broadband Symptom Complex", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1635654723", "stars": 5920, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 108, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 392937, "username": "CharlesGray", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/CharlesGray", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/38ee8199ec8ba2da6f194c14967f7561?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/38ee8199ec8ba2da6f194c14967f7561?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/38ee8199ec8ba2da6f194c14967f7561?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1552822171, "last_modified": 1665711156}, "last_reply_by": "lakehylia", "last_touched": 1665727097, "title": "心心念的千兆办下来了，现在很空虚", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/886823", "created": 1665711528, "deleted": 0, "content": "之前逛宽带症候群节点看见大家人手一个千兆 / 2.5G 就眼馋，心想着自己啥时候也有当机场测速员的资格。\r\n\r\n昨天终于把千兆办下来了，种种原因**只能**跑到 820Mb/s ，不过也很欣慰了。在 speedtest.net 和 speed.cloudflare.com 上花费了十几分钟之后合上电脑准备睡觉。\r\n\r\n闭着眼回味那个速度条噌噌窜的速度给我带来的快感，嘴角上扬，太美了。\r\n\r\n但立马发现：好像...平时确实用不到。\r\n\r\n我用 50MB/s 和 100MB/s 的区别貌似也就是下小姐姐们快一些，但平时也下不多...上行仍然只有 6MB/s ，把她们存到 Onedrive 的速度也没变化。\r\n\r\n开始回忆自己当时心里是不是为了千兆而千兆。这个千兆我办完了，好像在日常使用体验没咋提升的情况下，反而让我失去对千兆这个概念的向往。现在很空虚，不知道接下来该干啥。", "content_rendered": "<p>之前逛宽带症候群节点看见大家人手一个千兆 / 2.5G 就眼馋，心想着自己啥时候也有当机场测速员的资格。</p>\n<p>昨天终于把千兆办下来了，种种原因<strong>只能</strong>跑到 820Mb/s ，不过也很欣慰了。在 <a href=\"http://speedtest.net\" rel=\"nofollow\">speedtest.net</a> 和 <a href=\"http://speed.cloudflare.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">speed.cloudflare.com</a> 上花费了十几分钟之后合上电脑准备睡觉。</p>\n<p>闭着眼回味那个速度条噌噌窜的速度给我带来的快感，嘴角上扬，太美了。</p>\n<p>但立马发现：好像...平时确实用不到。</p>\n<p>我用 50MB/s 和 100MB/s 的区别貌似也就是下小姐姐们快一些，但平时也下不多...上行仍然只有 6MB/s ，把她们存到 Onedrive 的速度也没变化。</p>\n<p>开始回忆自己当时心里是不是为了千兆而千兆。这个千兆我办完了，好像在日常使用体验没咋提升的情况下，反而让我失去对千兆这个概念的向往。现在很空虚，不知道接下来该干啥。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1665711528, "replies": 60, "id": 886823}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_large.png?m=1595507885", "name": "ideas", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_normal.png?m=1595507885", "title": "奇思妙想", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/ideas", "topics": 5176, "footer": "", "header": "让你的创意在这里自由流动吧。", "title_alternative": "Ideas", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_mini.png?m=1595507885", "stars": 2681, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 519, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 592069, "username": "quehei", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/quehei", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/76d8/eec9/592069_mini.png?m=1661234361", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/76d8/eec9/592069_normal.png?m=1661234361", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/76d8/eec9/592069_large.png?m=1661234361", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/76d8/eec9/592069_xlarge.png?m=1661234361", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/76d8/eec9/592069_xlarge.png?m=1661234361", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/76d8/eec9/592069_xlarge.png?m=1661234361", "created": 1661234247, "last_modified": 1661234361}, "last_reply_by": "markzyh", "last_touched": 1665725859, "title": "打算跟女朋友求婚，兄弟们有一些好思路提供嘛", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/886708", "created": 1665656882, "deleted": 0, "content": "两家家长已经确认过了，打算过年回家的时候正式订婚宴➕过礼。\r\n所以年底之前我需要有一场求婚。预算是打算买一个 LV 的邮差包，然后装个 DR 的